data.description: Give your soul the serenity it desires without having to sacrifice any amenities of comfort. Whether you're sheltered by the custom stone fireplace with a cup of coffee enjoying panoramic views of the of the majestic Colorado skies, or relaxing as you bask in the rays of natural light in your sun room, or perhaps while you're soaking your worries away in your hot tub as you glance over open space, wondering if the greenhouse is ready to harvest, you'll never feel more at peace knowing you call this place home. Upon entering, the Great Room exudes tasteful elegance, showcasing seamless built-in cabinets and a captivating three-sided fireplace, enveloping the space in an inviting ambience. From there, the beautiful Brazilian hardwood floors flow into your gourmet kitchen as this culinary haven features a cozy breakfast nook, KitchenAid appliances, lustrous granite countertops, and a sprawling island inset with your concealed wine fridge. Revel in the conveniences of a spacious pantry closet and an integrated curio cabinet as you enjoy the views through bay windows overlooking your gourmet gas cooktop. Countless improvements and updates have been made to this home are too numerous to list, but the "piece de resistance" is an exquisite walk-in-master-closet, ornate with custom built-ins and a granite island as it's centerpiece, truly an oasis that is sure to fulfill the dreams or be the envy of any fashion-lover. You have to see it to believe it. Ideally located between within 10 miles of both Schriever SFB and Peterson SFB and only a 20 minute drive to the Air Force Academy, this spectacular home not only features a 3 car garage with... you guessed it- custom doors, it also boasts a huge concrete pad for your RV! A word of caution however to your RV: This will be your final destination. Sorry... your owners will no longer have use for you once they call this place home. They'll just never want to leave. Not convinced yet? Book your showing today and see for yourself!
